---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="About Us - Date Calculator Tools"
    description="Learn more about Date Calculator Tools, our privacy-centric browser-side execution philosophy, and our team."
>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">
            About Date Calculator Tools
        </h1>

        <div
            class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-base text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"
        >
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 font-medium">
                Welcome to <strong>Date Calculator Tools</strong>, your go-to
                online suite for clean, secure, and blazing-fast date
                calculations.
            </p>

            <p>
                In modern business and daily life, determining schedules,
                contract lengths, project sprint durations, or invoice deadlines
                is incredibly common yet surprisingly tedious. Many online tools
                are outdated, cluttered with heavy pop-up advertisements, slow
                to load, or force your information to be analyzed on external
                servers.
            </p>

            <p>
                We designed <strong>Date Calculator Tools</strong> with a clear, industrial
                philosophy: **utility, privacy, and speed**.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-10 mb-4">
                Our Core Philosophy
            </h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
                <div
                    class="border border-slate-200 p-5 rounded-xl bg-slate-50/50"
                >
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                        🔒 100% Client-Side
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        All date calculations are executed in memory using
                        standard browser-side JavaScript. Your dates are never
                        sent to our servers.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border border-slate-200 p-5 rounded-xl bg-slate-50/50"
                >
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                        ⚡ Blazing Fast
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        Because calculations run locally, there's zero network
                        latency. Click calculate and get results instantly.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="border border-slate-200 p-5 rounded-xl bg-slate-50/50"
                >
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">
                        📱 Responsive Design
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">
                        Our interfaces are meticulously styled to fit on mobile
                        phones, tablets, or multi-monitor desktop workspaces.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-10 mb-4">
                Who is this for?
            </h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 pl-4">
                <li>
                    <strong>Project Managers:</strong> To map milestones, sprint lengths,
                    and work days for agile planning.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Financial Professionals:</strong> To determine precise
                    Net 30, Net 60, or billing period calendar durations.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>HR Specialists:</strong> To count working business days
                    for timesheet validation and payroll cycles.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Event Planners:</strong> To schedule countdown tracks
                    leading up to weddings, product launches, or holidays.
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-10 mb-4">
                A Note on Holiday Calculations
            </h2>
            <p
                class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 text-amber-950 p-4 rounded-xl text-sm"
            >
                ⚠️ <strong>Important Notice:</strong> Our business days calculations
                (Monday-Friday) do not include localized public holidays in this version.
                Because federal, state, and bank holidays vary heavily by region,
                industry, and contract specification, we do not query a default holiday
                list to prevent calculation mistakes. Always review critical contract
                due dates manually.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-10 mb-4">
                Contact Us
            </h2>
            <p>
                We are constantly working to expand our date-utility
                capabilities. If you have suggestions for new calculation tools,
                custom feature designs, or noticed any calculation issues,
                please let us know via our <a
                    href="/contact/"
                    class="text-indigo-600 font-semibold hover:underline"
                    >Contact Page</a
                >.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
